<title>Alberto Dell'Era: Join Over Histograms</title>
<!--#include virtual="/ssi_post_title.html" -->
<br>
<br>This <a href="JoinOverHistograms.pdf">paper</a> presents and illustrates the formula used by the Oracle(TM) Cost Based Optimizer to estimate 
<br>the cardinality of an equijoin, when both the columns referenced in the join predicate have histograms collected.
<br>
<br>Practical implications (and possible pitfalls) are illustrated as well.
<br>
<br>The supporting material is <a href="JoinOverHistograms_supporting_material.zip">here</a>.

